data.title: Brooklyn Nets Roster
data.meta_description: Brooklyn Nets scores, news, schedule, players, stats, rumors, depth charts and more on RealGM.com
data.text:
Brook Lopez was selected as the #10 pick in the First Round of the 2008 NBA Draft by the New Jersey Nets. Brook Lopez signed a multi-year contract with the New Jersey Nets on July 2, 2008. Brook Lopez signed a multi-year contract with the Brooklyn Nets on July 11, 2012.

Mason Plumlee was selected as the #22 pick in the First Round of the 2013 NBA Draft by the Brooklyn Nets. Mason Plumlee signed a multi-year contract with the Brooklyn Nets on July 3, 2013.

Kevin Garnett was acquired in a trade by the Brooklyn Nets from the Boston Celtics on July 12, 2013.

Joe Johnson was acquired in a trade by the Brooklyn Nets from the Atlanta Hawks on July 11, 2012.

Paul Pierce was acquired in a trade by the Brooklyn Nets from the Boston Celtics on July 12, 2013.

Marquis Teague was acquired in a trade by the Brooklyn Nets from the Chicago Bulls on January 21, 2014.

Marcus Thornton was acquired in a trade by the Brooklyn Nets from the Sacramento Kings on February 19, 2014.

Deron Williams was acquired in a trade by the New Jersey Nets from the Utah Jazz on February 23, 2011. Deron Williams signed a multi-year contract with the Brooklyn Nets on July 11, 2012.

Alan Anderson signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Brooklyn Nets on July 30, 2013.

Andray Blatche signed a contract with the Brooklyn Nets on September 12, 2012. Andray Blatche re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Brooklyn Nets on July 11, 2013.

Jason Collins signed a contract with the Brooklyn Nets on February 23, 2014. Jason Collins re-signed to a contract as a free agent with the Brooklyn Nets on March 5, 2014. Jason Collins re-signed to a contract as a free agent with the Brooklyn Nets on March 15, 2014.

Jorge Gutierrez signed a contract with the Brooklyn Nets on March 6, 2014. Jorge Gutierrez re-signed to a contract as a free agent with the Brooklyn Nets on March 17, 2014. Jorge Gutierrez re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Brooklyn Nets on March 28, 2014.

Andrei Kirilenko signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Brooklyn Nets on July 12, 2013.

Shaun Livingston signed a contract as a free agent with the Brooklyn Nets on July 11, 2013.

Mirza Teletovic signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Brooklyn Nets on July 16, 2012.
